					"type": 23,
					"value": "Narrator/player to reading the plaque on Isobel's tomb . If they already know Isobel is Ketheric's daughter, the narrator reaction is different. The Elvish translates to 'Light slays darkness'.\r\n\r\nNote: the unusual structure of this is because the Origin PAD template is a greeting node and can't be connected to normally."
